a:7:{s:8:"encoding";s:5:"UTF-8";s:5:"title";s:38:"osCommerce News and Blog Announcements";s:4:"link";s:25:"http://www.oscommerce.com";s:11:"description";s:61:"An aggregated feed of osCommerce news and blog announcements.";s:8:"language";s:5:"en-us";s:5:"items";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:33:"osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3.1";s:4:"link";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,135";s:11:"description";s:1645:"<p>We're proud to announce the quick release of osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3.1! This release is a maintenance release bringing bug fixes and minor improvements.</p><b>Changes</b><p>The following changes are included in this release:</p><ul><li>Confirm new Product Reviews to the customer</li><li>Fix a PHP notice in Phpass</li><li>Fix Reviews Box language definition</li><li>Fix pre-defined Australian Dollar currency code</li><li>Label the HTML Content field for large product images</li><li>XHTML fixes for pop-up pages</li></ul><p><b>Files Updated</b></p><ul><li>catalog/admin/categories.php</li><li>catalog/admin/currencies.php</li><li>catalog/admin/includes/classes/passwordhash.php</li><li>catalog/admin/includes/languages/english/categories.php</li><li>catalog/includes/classes/passwordhash.php</li><li>catalog/includes/languages/english/product_reviews_write.php</li><li>catalog/includes/modules/boxes/bm_reviews.php</li><li>catalog/includes/version.php</li><li>catalog/info_shopping_cart.php</li><li>catalog/popup_image.php</li><li>catalog/popup_search_help.php</li><li>catalog/product_reviews.php</li><li>catalog/product_reviews_write.php</li></ul><p><b>Upgrade from v2.3.0 to v2.3.1</b></p><p>A detailed upgrade guide is included in the release and can also be read online at:</p><p><a href="http://www.oscommerce.info/confluence/display/OSCOM23/v2.3.0+to+v2.3.1">http://www.oscommerce.info/confluence/display/OSCOM23/v2.3.0+to+v2.3.1</a></p><b>Download</b><p>osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3.1 can be downloaded at:</p><p><a href="http://www.oscommerce.com/solutions/downloads">http://www.oscommerce.com/solutions/downloads</a></p>";s:4:"guid";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,135";s:7:"pubDate";s:31:"Sun, 14 Nov 2010 21:05:11 -0500";}i:1;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:31:"osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3";s:4:"link";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,134";s:11:"description";s:2560:"<p>We're extremely proud to announce the release of osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3! This release is an advancement to the previous v2.2 release series bringing security improvements, bug fixes, and new and exciting features to help strengthen and optimize your online store.</p><b>Features</b><p>New features in this release include:</p><ul><li>Modular Action Recorders to log and limit certain functions, including:<ul><li>Administration Tool login attempts</li><li>Tell A Friend e-mails</li><li>Contact Us e-mails</li></ul></li><li>Security Directory Permissions for the Administration Tool shows which directories are writable</li><li>Version Checker for the Administration Tool to check for new versions</li><li>Modular Social Bookmarks to share products on social sites, including:<ul><li>Facebook and Facebook Like</li><li>Twitter and Twitter Button</li><li>Google Buzz</li><li>Digg</li></ul></li><li>PayPal Express Checkout pre-configured for new store owners</li><li>Guest orders through PayPal Express Checkout</li><li>Modular Header Tags for optimizations, including:<ul><li>Google Analytics and E-Commerce Tracking</li><li>MailChimp E-Commerce 360</li><li>OpenSearch</li></ul></li><li>New separated XHTML/CSS based template</li><li>jQuery UI design</li><li>960 Grid System CSS Framework</li><li>Password hashing algorithm changed to Portable PHP hashing for customer and administrator passwords</li><li>Security Check modules for add-ons to check on server requirements</li><li>Administration Tool Dashboard widgets, including new charts</li><li>Modular Boxes to inject content anywhere in the HTML layout</li><li>Multiple Product Images with large images and HTML content for Flash videos</li><li>New Payment Modules, including:<ul><li>PayPal Website Payments Pro and PayPal Express Checkout</li><li>Moneybookers</li><li>Sage Pay</li></ul></li></ul><b>Download</b><p>Information on downloading osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3 can be found at:</p><p><a href="http://www.oscommerce.com/solutions/downloads">http://www.oscommerce.com/solutions/downloads</a></p><b>Add-Ons</b><p>We've strived to keep compatibility with over 6,000 existing add-ons for v2.2, and are now welcoming v2.3 optimized add-ons to the osCommerce Add-Ons site at:</p><p><a href="http://addons.oscommerce.com">http://addons.oscommerce.com</a></p><h2>Thank You!</h2><p>We'd like to thank each and every store owner, developer, enthusiast, and partner in the community for your continued support! <strong>Thank you!</strong> We wish you the best of business with this release!</p>";s:4:"guid";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,134";s:7:"pubDate";s:31:"Fri, 12 Nov 2010 22:14:37 -0500";}i:2;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:53:"Special Promotion for osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3";s:4:"link";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,133";s:11:"description";s:1925:"<p>We're excited to announce a special promotion for our Community and Corporate Sponsorship programs in anticipation of osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3 to be released this Friday, 12th November.</p><p>The Community Sponsorship program is now available for new and existing community members with a 50% discount for up to 12 months sponsorship. This opportunity is of great interest to community members where member profiles are specially highlighted in the community.</p><p><a href="http://www.oscommerce.com/partners/community">Click here to participate in the Community Sponsorship program.</a></p><p>The Corporate Sponsorship program is also now available for new and existing partners with a 50% discount on all levels for up to 3 months sponsorship. This opportunity is of great interest to developers, hosting providers, and service providers where e-commerce related services are promoted to the community.</p><p><a href="http://www.oscommerce.com/partners/corporate,info">Click here to sign up for the Corporate Sponsorship program.</a></p><p>This special promotion runs until the 30th November 2010. Don't miss out!</p><p>New features for osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3 include:</p><ul><li>Security Additions</li><li>Template based CSS Layout</li><li>Multiple Product Images and HTML Content (incl. Flash Videos)</li><li>PayPal Express Checkout preconfigured for new store owners</li><li>Header Tag Modules (incl. Google Analytics E-Commerce Tracking and MailChimp E-Commerce 360)</li><li>Social Bookmark Modules (incl. Facebook Like, Twitter Button, and Digg)</li><li>.. and more!</li></ul><p><a href="http://www.shinyredapples.com/post/1025216204/oscom-v2-3-pre-release-notes">Click here to find out what's new in the pre-release announcement.</a></p><p><a href="http://forums.oscommerce.com/topic/364291-oscommerce-v-23-when/">Click here to discuss the osCommerce Online Merchant v2.3 pre-announcement.</a></p>";s:4:"guid";s:40:"http://www.oscommerce.com/about/news,133";s:7:"pubDate";s:31:"Mon, 08 Nov 2010 16:38:17 -0500";}i:3;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:28:"OSCOM v2.3 Pre-Release Notes";s:4:"link";s:43:"http://blogs.oscommerce.com/post/1025226678";s:11:"description";s:606:"<a href="http://www.shinyredapples.com/post/1025216204/oscom-v2-3-pre-release-notes">OSCOM v2.3 Pre-Release Notes</a>: <p>Published by Harald Ponce de Leon</p>

